(44708, 72723, 3999, 15, '老煙斗-之謙接招自己的詞曲', '', '2012-02-17 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '＜老煙斗＞　詞：張之謙　2012.03.06\r\n\r\n時間不停淹過去　悄然無息\r\n淹過我的腳底　淹沒我的記性\r\n我守著一屋子的　老舊痕跡\r\n生活平靜　咬了一輩子的煙斗早熄\r\n\r\n習慣已成舊疾　我脫不去也好不起\r\n我鮮少回憶　因為也所剩無幾\r\n我漂浮於　時間的洪流之頂\r\n波濤之下　應該有你　和妳\r\n\r\n一件物品守著一段過去\r\n老邁如我　沉默成性\r\n偶然相遇　偶然沉溺\r\n妳的老酒杯　和我對飲\r\n乾杯　清脆如昔', '', 154, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-03-14 23:57:08', '2015-03-12 13:50:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44709, 140850, 0, 1, 'Bad Dream (that I can`t tell you)', '本來是要做一首器樂曲。\r\n也是我後來想要做的一個案子。\r\n專輯名 SLEEP(LESS)\r\n此曲排序第六。\r\n\r\n當初就是一直八小節循環的樂曲。\r\n曲名叫<不能知曉的惡夢>\r\n後來太喜歡這個歌名，就把歌詞寫好了。\r\n錄的時候幾乎就是即興發揮。', '2012-03-15 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'I have a bad dream since we have met \r\nIt reflects my secret, hidden by my pain\r\nI got no penny for wishing well\r\nGot no courage wishing for vainness\r\n\r\nIt`s a bad dream which always screws onto my skin\r\nFrom hurt to senseless .No way out but stand\r\nI got no chance, only an unwritten pen\r\nAll I have is my blank, say something flying on air\r\n\r\nIt`s only a bad dream. My past have predicted\r\nMy future is always an old play, old play, old game\r\nMy road is always on the same mistake. I`ve knew that, I know that\r\nA Dice with only pale. Such a fool with only a nightmare', '', 242, '', 'Azure Blighter', 'Azure Blighter', 'Azure Blighter', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-15 00:31:48', '2013-10-07 17:20:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44710, 140850, 0, 1, 'Dirty Hands', '我沒記錯的話，這應該是我大二寫的歌。\r\n編曲也極早就編了，也一直沒有改它的編曲。\r\n但錄音卻一直斷斷續續的。\r\n\r\n這首歌我另外有寫一個新詩的版本。\r\n', '2012-03-15 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 6, 'There she`ve gone\r\nSeven years        \r\nWhat could I know\r\nThe light are on\r\n\r\nMy dirty hands       \r\nNot shine like then \r\nMy dirty hands      \r\nBeg their beg \r\n\r\nInnocent           \r\nI saw my paper boat\r\nSo lies to me and   \r\nThrows  all of my case\r\n\r\nYour dirty hands   \r\nNot  shine like then\r\nMy dirty hands    \r\nWas with away\r\n', '', 172, '', 'Azure Blighter', 'Azure Blighter', 'Azure Blighter', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-15 00:32:18', '2013-10-07 17:20:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
